    "body" : "Don&#39;t confuse Locale with time zone. Totally separate. Locale determines human language for name of months and days, and cultural norms such as order of parts like month, day, etc. A time zone is offset-from-UTC plus rules for handling anomalies such as Daylight Saving Time."
