    "body" : "<p>I do it like this:</p>\n\n<pre><code>static String formatDate(long dateInMillis) {\n    Date date = new Date(dateInMillis);\n    return DateFormat.getDateInstance().format(date);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can also use <code>getDateInstance(int style)</code> with following parameters:</p>\n\n<p><code>DateFormat.SHORT</code></p>\n\n<p><code>DateFormat.MEDIUM</code></p>\n\n<p><code>DateFormat.LONG</code></p>\n\n<p><code>DateFormat.FULL</code></p>\n\n<p><code>DateFormat.DEFAULT</code></p>\n"
